videos.description: Skylar Thompson puts Kansas State on top 7-3 with a 3-yard touchdown run.

videos.description: Matt Campbell tells Roddy Jones that his team needs to pay more attention to detail in the second half.
videos.headline: Detail key for Iowa State in second half

videos.description: Kyle Kempt floats a pass up to Marchie Murdock who comes down with a touchdown for Iowa State.
videos.headline: Murdock reels in 9-yard TD

videos.description: Hakeem Butler catches a 3-yard touchdown from Kyle Kempt.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Butler grabs 3-yard TD

videos.description: Kansas State's Winston Dimel catches a touchdown on a halfback pass from running back Alex Barnes.
videos.headline: Barnes throws jump pass TD to Dimel

videos.description: Anish Shroff and Ahmad Brooks break down Kansas State's last second 20-19 win over Iowa State.
videos.headline: Kansas State tops Iowa State in a thriller
